### Title: What is Digital Literacy?
Tool used: Canva 
Created by: (Aarush  / 25 batch )

- About this presentation:
This resource introduces the concept of Digital Literacy — the ability to find, evaluate, and communicate information using digital devices and media. It covers three core competencies (Comprehension, Critical Thinking, and Content Creation), highlights useful tools for students (GitHub, Canva, LinkedIn), and guides viewers on building a professional online presence.
